even without getting married.

1064
01:09:53,000 --> 01:09:55,410
- Indu, what are you saying?
- The truth.

1065
01:09:56,560 --> 01:10:00,080
Indu, you may say
whatever you like about me.

1066
01:10:00,160 --> 01:10:02,620
But there is no need to
speak about DK this way.

1067
01:10:03,520 --> 01:10:04,790
There was a need, so I spoke.

1068
01:10:05,320 --> 01:10:06,320
Meaning?

1069
01:10:08,520 --> 01:10:10,280
You can ask him that!

1070
01:10:11,280 --> 01:10:13,590
Hey! What's wrong
with her? ...Indu!

1071
01:10:14,140 --> 01:10:15,980
(Dog barks at distance)

1072
01:10:18,880 --> 01:10:20,010
What's the matter?

1073
01:10:21,920 --> 01:10:25,080
I've been observing this tension
between you since morning.

1074
01:10:26,520 --> 01:10:29,930
And the way Indu was
talking to that boy Rahul...

1075
01:10:30,960 --> 01:10:32,750
Who is Rahul?

1076
01:10:37,080 --> 01:10:39,120
- He is my son.
- What!

1077
01:10:44,900 --> 01:10:46,000
He is my son

1078
01:10:46,160 --> 01:10:47,350
(Sighs)

1079
01:10:47,440 --> 01:10:49,970
When I went to Nainital in 1973...

1080
01:10:50,010 --> 01:10:52,370
(Cheering)

1081
01:10:56,080 --> 01:10:57,720
- No, I won't have.
- You're grown up now!

1082
01:10:57,800 --> 01:11:00,320
- You're going to be a father!
- Get lost!

1083
01:11:00,640 --> 01:11:03,480
