even married as yet!

1084
01:11:03,510 --> 01:11:05,200
(Indistinct)

1085
01:11:06,880 --> 01:11:11,070
In the midst of the din, she too
was there... lonely and quiet.

1086
01:11:12,400 --> 01:11:16,120
Her name was Bhavna.
I knew her from my school days.

1087
01:11:16,440 --> 01:11:19,680
She used to be so lively.
But now...

1088
01:11:20,040 --> 01:11:22,700
This girl has been through a big tragedy.

1089
01:11:23,160 --> 01:11:26,920
She lost her family in a car
accident while still in school.

1090
01:11:27,480 --> 01:11:31,680
The master said that Bhavna had
completely withdrawn since then.

1091
01:11:32,840 --> 01:11:35,520
The master knew Bhavna and
her family since a long time...

1092
01:11:35,550 --> 01:11:38,430
